videos.description: Quentin Goodwin feeds a pass to Tyrique Jones who powers in a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Jones abuses the rim on dunk

videos.description: Xavier's Trevon Bluiett dishes a nice pass then later spins around a defender for a difficult jump shot.
videos.headline: Bluiett uses a nifty spin to set up a jumper

videos.description: Jon Elmore creates contact and still makes the difficult layup as Marshall goes on a 10-0 scoring run early in the second half.
videos.headline: Elmore makes tough layup to add to Marshall's 10-0 run

videos.description: Jon Elmore slices through the Xavier defense for a layup with some fancy footwork.
videos.headline: Elmore Eurosteps through the lane for layup
